text: Anders Lindh (2 October 1929 - 19 November 1996) was a Swedish gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1929 births Category:1996 deaths Category:Swedish male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Sweden Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Örebro
